    m_Alignment: 3
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "Two voodoo dolls enter. Only one leaves intact.\n\nCombat:\nLight Attack
    \u2014 quick jab\nHeavy Attack \u2014 slow but hits hard\nBlock \u2014 hold to
    reduce incoming damage\nFirst to drain the opponent's health triggers a Killer
    Shot\n\n\nKiller Shot:\nWhen a player's health drops low, a reaction prompt appears.
    Press the reaction button as fast as you can \u2014 whoever reacts first wins
    the exchange and knocks the opponent down.\n\n\nKnockdown:\nThe downed player
    must mash the get-up button to recover before time runs out. Meanwhile the attacker
    can hold Block to pull the downed player's arm \u2014 pull it far enough and
    they lose their heavy attack for the rest of the round.\n\n\nWinning:\nFirst
    to win 2 rounds wins the match."
